{"title":"BigData-HDFS","slug":"BigData-HDFS","date":"2023-03-09","updated":"2023-03-15","comments":true,"path":"api/posts/32491.json","excerpt":"<blockquote><p> 关于 HDFS 的相关操作 </p></blockquote>","cover":null,"covers":null,"content":"<blockquote>\n<p>关于 HDFS 的相关操作</p>\n</blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h1 id=\"文件操作命令\"><a href=\"# 文件操作命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"文件操作命令\"></a>文件操作命令 </h1><p><strong> 创建文件</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>hdfs dfs -mkdir -p <Path></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>显示目录</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>hdfs dfs -ls /</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>文件上传</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>-f 是强制覆盖<br>hdfs dfs -put [-f][-p] <localsrc> <dst></li>\n<li>文件合并后上传<br>hdfs dfs -appendToFile /root/opt/<em>.</em> /user/root/txtdir/merge.txt</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>文件下载</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li>hdfs 中文件合并后下载<br>hdfs dfs -getmerge /user/root/txtdir/<em>.</em> /root/opt/join.txt</li>\n<li>直接从 hdfs 下载文件到本地<br>hdfs dfs -get /user/root/a.txt /root/opt/join.txt</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>文件内容查询</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>hdfs dfs -cat /user/root/txtdir/a.txt</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>文件删除</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>hdfs dfs -rm <path></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"web 界面操作\"><a href=\"#web 界面操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"web 界面操作\"></a>web 界面操作</h1><h2 id=\"hdfs 查看\"><a href=\"#hdfs 查看\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"hdfs 查看\"></a>hdfs 查看</h2><blockquote>\n<p>master:50075</p>\n</blockquote>\n","url":"/posts/32491/","min2read":"1","word4post":137,"prev_post":{"title":"AC-windowsWords","url":"/posts/46298/"},"next_post":{"title":"BigData-Hadoop","url":"/posts/30565/"},"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"文件操作命令\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">文件操作命令 </span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"web 界面操作\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">web 界面操作</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" data-id=\"hdfs 查看\" href = \"#\"><span class=\"toc-number\">2.1.</span> <span class=\"toc-text\">hdfs 查看</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","categories":[{"name":"Bigdata","path":"api/categories/Bigdata.json","url":"/categories/Bigdata/"}],"tags":[]}